<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Purge Failed</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: #333; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px;">
    <h2 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #c0392b;">[ACTION REQUIRED] Account purge failed</h2>

    <p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0;">A scheduled account-deletion job failed and the account was NOT purged. Manual investigation is required to ensure the user's data is handled per policy.</p>

    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 14px;">
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: 600; width: 40%;">Job ID</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 12px; font-family: monospace;">{{jobId}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: 600;">Account ID</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 12px; font-family: monospace;">{{accountId}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: 600;">Occurred at</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 12px;">{{occurredAt}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: 600; vertical-align: top;">Error</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 12px; font-family: monospace; word-break: break-all;">{{errorMessage}}</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #666;">Check the deletion_audit_logs table and BullMQ dashboard for the full stack trace. A PURGE_FAILED event has been written to the audit log.</p>
  </body>
</html>
